CONFRONTATIONS; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; MEETINGS; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; BUSH, GEORGE; WAR; POWELL, COLIN L 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
