<DATELINE>
<P>
SAO PAULO, Brazil 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Assailants shot and killed rural union leader Jose Helio da Silva who had 
defied powerful sugar barons in northeastern Brazil, police said Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
MURDERS -- BRAZIL; BRAZIL -- LABOR 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
