<P>
Matsushita Secures MCA Funds: Matsushita Electric Industrial Co. said it has 
lined up most of the financing needed to complete its $6.59-billion purchase of 
MCA Inc. The funding package is being assembled by a Matsushita subsidiary, 
Panasonic Finance Inc. Financing reportedly will come from a variety of local 
and foreign lenders. The Japanese company plans to contribute an additional $1 
billion from its own cash reserves. 
