Golden West 102, Fullerton 89 -- Scott Campbell, a transfer from Cal State 
Fullerton, scored a game-high 32 points for Golden West (6-8), which advances 
to the consolation championship at 1 p.m. today. Fullerton (8-6) is eliminated. 
</P>
<P>
Campbell was 13 of 21 from the field, including four of seven three-point 
tries, and Golden West shot 59% (38 of 69) for the game. Ric Van Scoyoc added 
22 points and 12 assists for Golden West. 
</P>
<P>
Bob Terry scored 26 and Gary Hunter 18 for Fullerton. 
