give host Fullerton a 54-51 lead. Nicki Durity scored 20 points to lead 
Fullerton (10-2). 
</P>
<P>
Citrus 61, Cypress 60 -- Chris Bazzel scored 21 points and had 10 rebounds for 
Cypress (1-11). 
