<HEADLINE>
<P>
CLIPBOARD; 
</P>
<P>
LESS FILLING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The number of gas service stations has steadily decreased over the last five 
years in Orange County. However, taxable sales at the stations during the same 
period have fluctuated, including an 11% jump in 1989. The number of service 
stations in the county and their taxable sales are detailed below. 
</P>
